Cardiff Blues and Ospreys go-head-to-head in the 14:30 BST kick-off live on BBC Two Wales and online as the two rivals bid for a European Champions Cup place.
Newport Gwent Dragons play Scarlets in the 17:00 BST kick-off live on S4C as the Llanelli region hope to secure their European Champions Cup qualification.
